### By creating strategic partnerships, we can support those living with or
affected by diabetes, while also helping your company achieve its objectives
Diabetes affects millions of people in the UK, including your employees and
customers. With someone diagnosed every two minutes, we need to act now **.**
Your support will help us fund our crucial work.
Tesco and Boots are just two of our current partners.
